<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2913359909203054532">Harper Bliss is a best-selling lesbian romance author. Among her most-loved books are the highly dramatic French Kissing and the often thought-provoking Pink Bean series. She is the co-founder of My LesFic, a weekly newsletter offering discount deals on lesbian fiction.<br/><br/>Harper lived in Hong Kong for 7 years, travelled the world for a bit, and has now settled in Brussels (Belgium) with her wife and </span>
  <span id="freeText2913359909203054532" style="display:none">Harper Bliss is a best-selling lesbian romance author. Among her most-loved books are the highly dramatic French Kissing and the often thought-provoking Pink Bean series. She is the co-founder of My LesFic, a weekly newsletter offering discount deals on lesbian fiction.<br /><br />Harper lived in Hong Kong for 7 years, travelled the world for a bit, and has now settled in Brussels (Belgium) with her wife and photogenic cat, Dolly Purrton.<br /><br />Together with her wife, she hosts a weekly podcast called Harper Bliss &amp; Her Mrs.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2913359909203054532" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

